WEBVTT

00:00.836 --> 00:04.718
There were reports of an earthquake near North Korea's nuclear testing site.

00:05.741 --> 00:09.709
This was followed by a North Korea state television special announcement...

00:10.331 --> 00:13.341
...saying it successfully tested a Hydrogen bomb.

00:14.556 --> 00:18.569
Japan and South Korea promised to punish North Korea for their actions.

00:19.376 --> 00:22.336
The United States have spoken against the test...

00:22.386 --> 00:25.292
...but are still trying to prove North Korea's claim.

